description:
When Sleet and Dingo attempt to change their dastardly ways in favor of the side of good, they flee from the evil Doctor Robotnik and spend the night at the home of Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin's personal bitch, Sonic the Hedghog. Sleet and Dingo assume they are safe, but those who try and defy Doctor Robotnik will always pay a heavy price.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uAz9Stwz3Fg
